  <source>Wyeth is now a wholly owned subsidiary of Pfizer</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to compare the efficacy and tolerance of piperacillin-tazobactam
      versus piperacillin-tazobactam plus glycopeptide as initial empiric antibiotic treatment for
      fever in neutropenic patients. Study of consecutive cohorts(2). First the patients will be
      included in the monotherapy branch until completing the predicted number of cases. When this
      happens, the Coordinating Center will communicate it to the participant centers and from then
      the patients will be included in the combined therapy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
